wikipedia_page.main: Ryan James Adams (born 11 March 1993) is an English first-class cricketer. He is a right handed batsman. He made his first-class debut for Cardiff MCCU against Glamorgan.

response: Ryan Adams (born 1974) is an American singer-songwriter, record producer, and poet.
